        <Parent_String>printing surface preparation tools [300233611], printing surface preparation equipment [300233609], equipment for printing and printmaking [300167852], image-making equipment [300162803], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
